Author: cinnamonbicycle
Text: Hey, I know the feeling, and I'm sorry you're in that place right now. Try to drink something so at least you're hydrated, and maybe take a few vitamin supplements if you have any on hand. Salt can be a good idea to keep your electrolytes in balance, too. If you feel able to eat at any point, start with something very safe. Be patient with yourself, but do your best to eat all of it, whatever it is. Try to take care of yourself, OP <3
